data.description: Offering budget-conscious home buyers the opportunity to have a single-family home that has a garage and private yard, all without the expense of an HOA!  Inside, you'll appreciate the large kitchen with ample cabinet and countertop space and the area next to the fridge could accommodate a hutch or shelving unit to add even more storage or organizational options.  A fireplace and accent wall make the living area feel cozy and welcoming to your family and guests. The bedrooms are upstairs and the primary room has an ensuite with a walk-in closet. The 2 car garage and space under the stairs provide storage solutions that make the home a great fit for many homeowners.  The backyard is fully enclosed and accessible by a side gate. This home has been owner-occupied and is well-maintained.
